courses.desc: If you had to choose one thing to be good at in order to be successful in arena, it's to deal as much damage as possible.

courses.title: USE LINE OF SIGHT TO YOUR ADVANTAGE
courses.desc: How to make correct use of line of sight.

courses.desc: Understand what it means to overextend and when you can do it, how to position differently when playing melee caster and double caster and how to make the most of pillars to avoid crowd control while healing.

courses.title: WIN MORE GAMES BY PLAYING AROUND COOLDOWNS
courses.desc: Learn when to trade, how to avoid overlapping and how to capitalize enemy cooldown usage.
